import Myimg from "../../images/svg-1.svg";

export const homeObj = {
  id: "about",
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: "NEW SOLUTION",
  headline: "YOUR NEXT STEP AHEAD.",
  description:
    "We use social media to tell you things that you could not see before.",
  buttonLable: "GET STARTED",
  imgStart: false,
  img: require("../../images/svg-1.svg"),
  alt: "twitter",
  dark: false,
  primary: true,
  darkText: true,
};
